GEO TARGETED BUSINESS ADVERTISING SYSTEM

To build a business advertising system that shows particular ads for a particular niche blog and specific location.

-Though Google Adsense,Mediavine ad systems target people based on their interests. Still, we can skyrocket the conversion rates with high values by showing the specific local business ads for specific content and specific location. We can also put a quarterly bidding system for advertisers if more than one advertiser applies for the same niche and locality.

-Here, our system acts as a platform for advertisers to market their products/services to their local audiences who’re looking for a solution in their category. Our system intelligently shows the particular set of ads from local agencies to the viewers viewing the websites/blogs in the same locality and content. Our system has two user categories i.e., publishers and advertisers. Publishers own blogs/websites with huge traffic and advertisers own businesses who’re wishing to market their services/products to local audiences by
putting their ads on corresponding publisher’s blogs/websites in the same category. We’ll also include a payment gateway through which advertisers can pay to the platform. 

-Our main service categories include but not limited to Home automation business, Wifi business, Home decoration, Soundproofing business, Laundry business.
